value.name: Tarraleah Power Station - Wikipedia
value.snippet: Power station The outdoor switchyard located adjacent to the Tarraleah Power Station. Part of the Derwent scheme that now comprises eleven hydroelectric power stations, the Tarraleah Power Station is located aboveground on the west bank of the Nive River downstream from the village of Tarraleah and a short distance from the Lyell Highway .
